## Key Concepts
- Tenant-based routing and isolation
- SageMaker Endpoints vs Serverless Inferencing
- Feature Store and Model Registry per tenant
- PrivateLink, data residency, and retention policies
- Canary rollout, drift monitoring, automatic rollback

